Package com.seailz.discordjv.model.guild

Record Class UnavailableGuild

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.seailz.discordjv.model.guild.UnavailableGuild
Record Components:
id - The id of the guild
name - The name of the guild
icon - The icon hash of the guild
splash - The splash hash of the guild
discoverySplash - The discovery splash hash of the guild
emojis - The emojis of the guild
features - The list of GuildFeature the guild has
approximateMemberCount - The approximate number of members in the guild
approximatePresenceCount - The approximate number of online members in the guild
description - The description of the guild
stickers - A list of Sticker objects that the guild has
All Implemented Interfaces:
Compilerable
public record UnavailableGuild(String id, String name, String icon, String splash, String discoverySplash, List<Emoji> emojis, List<GuildFeature> features, int approximateMemberCount, int approximatePresenceCount, String description, List<Sticker> stickers) extends Record implements Compilerable
Represents an unavailable guild. These are usually created during the READY event.
